Coloration in alcohol. Dorsal surface dark brown on head to light brown on margins of trunk (juveniles lighter than adults). Ventral surface light brown to yellow in juveniles. Body and fins covered by scattered chromatophores, which are more visible on dorsal and lateral portions of head (
